statements: SELECT * FROM RentalData;
SELECT rental_id, property_address FROM RentalData ORDER BY rental_id DESC;
SELECT property_address, rental_income FROM RentalData WHERE rental_income > 5000;
SELECT rental_id, profit_margin FROM RentalData ORDER BY profit_margin ASC;
SELECT * FROM RentalData WHERE property_expenses BETWEEN 1000 AND 2000;
SELECT rental_id, property_address, rental_income, property_expenses, profit_margin FROM RentalData WHERE rental_income > 2000 ORDER BY property_address DESC
SELECT rental_id, property_address, rental_income, property_expenses, profit_margin FROM RentalData WHERE profit_margin < 0.5 ORDER BY rental_id ASC
SELECT count(rental_id) as number_of_rentals, sum(rental_income) as total_income, avg(profit_margin) as average_margin FROM RentalData WHERE property_expenses < 1000 GROUP BY property_address
SELECT rental_id, property_address, rental_income, property_expenses, profit_margin FROM RentalData WHERE property_expenses > rental_income * 0.2 ORDER BY profit_margin DESC, property_address ASC
SELECT rental_id, property_address, rental_income, property_expenses, profit_margin FROM RentalData WHERE profit_margin < 0.3 OR property_expenses > 1500 ORDER BY rental_income DESC
SELECT * FROM RentalIncome;
SELECT property_id, rental_amount, rental_date FROM RentalIncome;
SELECT rental_id, property_id, rental_amount FROM RentalIncome WHERE rental_amount > 1000;
SELECT expense_id, property_id, expense_amount, expense_type FROM Expenses WHERE expense_amount < 500;
SELECT * FROM RentalIncome JOIN Expenses ON RentalIncome.property_id = Expenses.property_id;
SELECT * FROM RentalIncome WHERE rental_amount > 1000 ORDER BY rental_date DESC;
SELECT property_id, SUM(rental_amount) AS total_rent FROM RentalIncome GROUP BY property_id ORDER BY total_rent DESC;
SELECT property_id, COUNT(*) AS total_expenses FROM Expenses GROUP BY property_id HAVING total_expenses > 5;
SELECT rental_id, rental_amount, rental_date FROM RentalIncome INNER JOIN Properties ON RentalIncome.property_id = Properties.property_id WHERE Properties.city = 'New York' ORDER BY rental_date ASC;

SELECT property_id, expense_type, SUM(expense_amount) AS total_expense FROM Expenses WHERE expense_date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-12-31' GROUP BY property_id, expense_type ORDER BY total_expense DESC;
SELECT * FROM rental_income ORDER BY rental_date DESC;
SELECT rental_id, rental_amount FROM rental_income WHERE rental_amount > 1000;
SELECT property_id, rental_amount FROM rental_income WHERE rental_amount BETWEEN 500 AND 1000;
SELECT * FROM expenses WHERE expense_type='Maintenance' AND expense_amount < 500;
SELECT property_id, profit_percentage FROM profit_margin ORDER BY profit_percentage DESC;
SELECT * FROM rental_income WHERE property_id = '4567ef21-12ab-4cde-890f-98abc7654321' AND rental_amount > 1000 ORDER BY rental_date DESC
SELECT rental_id, rental_amount FROM rental_income WHERE rental_amount BETWEEN 500 AND 1000 ORDER BY rental_date ASC
SELECT property_id, SUM(expense_amount) AS total_expense FROM expenses WHERE expense_date > '2022-01-01' GROUP BY property_id HAVING total_expense > 5000
SELECT property_id, AVG(profit_percentage) AS avg_profit FROM profit_margin WHERE profit_date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-12-31' GROUP BY property_id ORDER BY avg_profit DESC

SELECT rental_id, property_id, rental_amount, profit_percentage FROM rental_income ri JOIN profit_margin pm ON ri.property_id = pm.property_id WHERE rental_date > '2022-06-01' AND profit_date < rental_date ORDER BY rental_amount DESC, profit_percentage ASC
SELECT * FROM RentalIncome;
SELECT rental_id, rental_amount, rent_start_date FROM RentalIncome ORDER BY rent_start_date DESC;
SELECT property_id, SUM(rental_amount) AS total_rent FROM RentalIncome GROUP BY property_id;
SELECT * FROM Expenses WHERE expense_date >= '2022-01-01' AND expense_date <= '2022-12-31';
SELECT property_id, MAX(profit_amount) AS max_profit FROM ProfitMargins;
SELECT * FROM RentalIncome ORDER BY rental_amount DESC, rent_end_date
SELECT property_id, rental_amount FROM RentalIncome WHERE rent_start_date >= '2022-01-01'
SELECT property_id, profit_amount FROM ProfitMargins WHERE profit_amount > 5000
SELECT * FROM Expenses WHERE expense_type LIKE '%tax%'
SELECT property_id, decision_type FROM InvestmentDecisions ORDER BY decision_date ASC
SELECT * FROM RentalIncome ORDER BY id ASC LIMIT 5;
SELECT property_id, rental_amount FROM RentalIncome WHERE rental_date >= '2022-01-01' ORDER BY rental_date DESC;
SELECT id, expense_type, expense_amount FROM Expenses WHERE expense_amount > 1000 ORDER BY id;

SELECT property_id, rental_amount, rental_date FROM RentalIncome WHERE rental_amount > 1000;
